<img src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/V_Esposito-b.jpg" alt width height border="1" />
<br/>
<div class="phototagleft">
Photo by Kristin Cofer
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Veronica Esposito</b> is an associate marriage and family therapist specializing in serving transgender individuals and a regular contributor to venues including <i>The Guardian, Xtra Magazine</i>, and San Francisco NPR affiliate KQED. She was a judge for the 2022 National Book Award in Translation.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
